content: Great app!!! But..... If you could work to make the dial start/stop Angle adjustment individually on each gauge will reach perfection level . I will happy to pay again if necessary to make you do this option possible and I think everyone who likes to play trying get the perfect theme will agreed this detail will be the final key . I'm still giving 5 stars because app works like a champ .thanks

bought torque pro. it works fine. bought this theme pack. applied theme. restarted torque software and no theme change. great stuff. glad I bought it while still in my car so I beat the refund window.
Not to bad,a bit buggy on a couple of the themes.
Thanks to the developer. Many options and the ability to create my own theme(s)/gauges.
So many....  All look good. The hard part is picking one..
